{"tid":1509023,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"曱甴全家速速去死","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:14:26.000Z","uid":266270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d81b804a1aab1d006fe61fdc0c10e4344453b9f","tid":1509023,"uid":266270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"其實大家認為曱甴係一種點樣嘅生物？<br />\n<br />\n對大眾而言，曱甴係「害蟲」，外表嚇人又傳播細菌令人生病作嘔，大部分正常人見到曱甴第一時間嘅反應都係喊打喊殺。咁我想問而家係社會上，有咩人喺條街度行下都會畀人唾罵？有乜嘢人可以同冇人性冇道德嘅曱甴相提並論呢？<br />\n而眾所周知，狗係人類最好嘅朋友，佢哋好多嘅行動都證明咗佢哋有同理心會去幫助同安慰佢哋飼養者。<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅稱呼居然係反轉咗，真係可笑。所以麻煩大家用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴</span></strong></span>稱呼返佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n一來見到一班<span style=\"color: red;\">社會垃圾</span>咁樣話人，我相信大家心裡都好唔平衡。我哋更加可以利用返呢個佢哋自己接受咗係<span style=\"color: red;\">貶義</span>嘅代名詞嚟<span style=\"color: red;\">以其人之道還治其人之身</span>，令到佢哋明白自己嘅身份，增加佢哋嘅心理壓力。<br />\n<br />\n知法犯法？但他們根本不知法<br />\n黑社會？有牌古惑仔你知佢都知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察，你係曱甴！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee6457709c2d84627011a225673fda00179829da","tid":1509023,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=986a1c44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f16a49e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/